title: Stylish private cabanas, Ceiling fans included, Spacious 9' ceilings

posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Individually controlled heating and air conditioning with Nest thermostats', '-Dacora rocker switches and USB outlets in the living room and bedrooms', '-Washer and dryer in every residence', '-Cutting edge fitness studio with cardio, strength training, Fitness On Demand and yoga studio', '-Floor-to-ceiling windows for an abundance of natural light in select residences', '-Designer lighting and plumbing fixtures', '-Kitchen islands with designer pendant lighting in select floorplans', '-Signature two and three bedroom townhome floor plans with 2-car garages and penthouse level residences available', '-Additional premium storage space available', '-Amazing views of Boca Raton, the Boca Raton Country Club and beaches from upper level residences', '-Dog park and dog wash station for our 4-legged residents', '-51-bottle wine cooler in most residences', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
